<div class="sub-content-header">Innovations 2012 Design and Engineering Awards Call For Judges Opening Soon</div>
<br />

<IMG style="MARGIN-TOP: 0px; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px" hspace=5 align=right src="/images/content/2K12Innovations_SAMPLE.jpg" width=101 height=150>Every year the CE industry lights up with new innovative designs and products, and thousands of industry leaders and press flock to CES to witness the "<A href="/exhibitors/newsletter/2010.asp">next big thing</A>." Do you think you know what’s best? Let the world know!<BR><BR>The Innovations <A href="/exhibitors/newsletter/callForJudges.asp">Call for Judges</A> opens July 25, 2011. If you're an independent designer or an engineer, <A href="/exhibitors/newsletter/callForJudges.asp">we want you</A>! Qualified exhibitors are eligible to judge categories in which their employers have not entered products. Be the first to see the newest products in the CE industry!<BR><BR>The <A href="/awards/default.asp">International CES<SUP>®</SUP> Innovations 2012 Design and Engineering Awards</A> is the most impressive and renowned awards program in the consumer technology industry. Being an Innovations Honoree can provide exhibitors with incredible opportunities, special recognition in the CE industry and worldwide exposure for your company and products. Help out your industry, and <A href="/exhibitors/newsletter/callForJudges.asp">sign up to be a judge</A>.<BR><br />
